data.description: Cute and cozy updated cottage in the highly desired area of Mossy Oaks. This one story brick ranch rests on a large corner homesite and is only minutes from downtown Beaufort, Port Royal and Parris Island. The property is further complimented by a large screen porch, fresh half bathroom addition, new paint, fully fenced rear yard and new plumbing. Your Lowcountry cottage is finally here.
